            "title": "美元變動不大　美長債息反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美元變動不大，市場等待周五公布的美國通脹數據。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在紐約尾市，美元指數報98.93。美元兌日圓升0.4%，較早時報152.58日圓。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐元兌美元升近0.1%，英鎊兌美元跌0.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，美國長債息率連跌3日後反彈，美國對俄羅斯的制裁推高油價，市場預計通脹將於中短期內上升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">10年期債息突破4厘，高見4.007厘，30年期債息高見4.593厘，兩者都升逾5個基點，其後稍為回順。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15367091-%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7%e3%80%80%e7%be%8e%e9%95%b7%e5%82%b5%e6%81%af%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240410_source-licensed_USD_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 08:05:23",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
