            "title": "中鐵建首三季新簽合同按年升逾3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國鐵建(01186)公布，第三季新簽合同總額4625.954億元( 人民幣‧下同)，首9個月新簽合同總額15187.65億元，按年增3.08%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">房地產開發方面，第三季析簽合同總額174.88億元，首9月新簽合同總額542.71億元，按年減11.53%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15365869-%e4%b8%ad%e9%90%b5%e5%bb%ba%e9%a6%96%e4%b8%89%e5%ad%a3%e6%96%b0%e7%b0%bd%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be3",
